<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LibraryEntry xmlns="http://exocad.com/model/attachment">
	<Supplier>exocad GmbH</Supplier>
	<DisplayInformation>Transversal Connector</DisplayInformation>
	<AttachmentPreviewFileName>preview.png</AttachmentPreviewFileName>
	<SupplierLogoFileName>logo.png</SupplierLogoFileName>
	<AttachmentDescription>
	
Geometry for addition to upper or lower jaw model. Can be used to stabilize models.
 
- Adjustable Width in X direction (between 30-60mm).
- Adjustable Size in Z direction.  
- Free positioning in X/Y, rotatable along Z.

</AttachmentDescription>	
	<Placement  Move="XY" Rotate="Z" Jaw="Any">
		<Translation Axis="XY" Ref="_clickpoint" DirRef="_clickpoint">
			<Const>0.0</Const>
		</Translation>
	</Placement>
	<Parameter Scope="All" Default="0" Min="0" Max="10" Unit="%" Decimals="1">Size</Parameter>
	<Parameter Scope="Single" Default="0" Min="-15" Max="15" Unit="mm" Decimals="1">Width</Parameter>	
	<Component IfJaw="Any" Method="AdditiveOmittingCavities"  >
		<MeshFile FileName="traversal45.eoff" >
			<Translation Axis="Z">
				<Const>4.55</Const>
			</Translation>		
			<Select Label="CUSP_1" >
				<Scaling Axis="Z">
					<ParameterRef Coefficient="0.11111111">Size</ParameterRef>
					<Const>1</Const>					
				</Scaling>
			</Select>
			<Select Label="CUSP_2" >
				<Scaling Axis="X">
					<ParameterRef Coefficient="0.0222222">Width</ParameterRef>
					<Const>1</Const>					
				</Scaling>
			</Select>			
		</MeshFile>
		<mat:Material xmlns:mat="http://exocad.com/config/color">
			<mat:Color>#453B6A</mat:Color>
		</mat:Material>
		<Alignment Jaw="Any" RelativeToBottom="true" AutoFlip="true"/>
	</Component>	
</LibraryEntry>